<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <%- include('../../partials/head.ejs') %>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white">
    <%- include('../../partials/nav.ejs') %>
    <%- include('../../partials/topNav.ejs') %>

    <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0 md:ml-64">
      <div class="md:py-8 mx-5 sm:mx-8 lg:mx-14 xl:mx-20"> 
        <div class="py-6 lg:py-10 bg-white lg:border">
          <div class="mx-5 lg:px-6">
            <div>
              <img class="w-32" src="/assets/images/CSR-A_Logo-RGB.jpg" alt="logo" />
            </div>
          </div>  
          
          <div class="mx-5 lg:px-6 pb-5 text-justify text-sm lg:text-base">
            <div class="pt-8">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-mono text-[#00A19A]">SECTION ONE - ENVIRONMENT</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-7">
              <p class="pt-4 font-bold">ENVIRONMENT - 1E/ Waste</p>

              <p class="pt-4">
                Do you implement and monitor saving initiatives? What statistics, targets/KPIs and reductions have you made? What are
                the financial benefits and measurable impacts? Have you/your colleagues demonstrated commitment to initiatives? What
                ideas do you have to improve?
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-sm">Please use the list below to prompt your thinking.</h4>

              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 pt-3">
                <li class="pl-5">
                  Recycle paper and cardboard.
                </li>

                <li class="pl-5 pt-2">
                  Recycle, repair, reuse office equipment - furniture, computers etc.
                </li>

                <li class="pl-5 pt-2">
                  Plastics - source alternative materials, repair, reuse, recycle.
                </li>

                <li class="pl-5 pt-2">
                  Zero waste to landfill statement/goal.
                </li>

                <li class="pl-5 pt-2">
                  Reducing, reusing, recycling statement in place.
                </li>

                <li class="pl-5 pt-2">
                  Food waste reduction - anaerobic digestion â€“ do you compost appropriate items?
                </li>

                <li class="pl-5 pt-2">
                  Hazardous waste management - including but not limited to: Aerosols Adhesives Management policies for: Industrial
                  Solvents, Waste Electrical and Electronic Equipment (WEEE) Fluorescent tubes, Batteries, Laboratory and Bulk Chemicals,
                  Acids, Washings, Rags, wipes, Contaminated Packaging, Pharmaceuticals, Paint, Oil, Asbestos, Sanitary Waste.
                </li>

                <li class="pl-5 pt-2">
                  Prevention of pollution - discharges to water, waste management, use and disposal of toxic and hazardous chemicals,
                  other identifiable forms of pollution.
                </li>

                <li class="pl-5 pt-2">
                  Please show statistical data where available.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>  

            <form class="pt-5">
              <textarea id="env_waste" class="p-8 max-h-96 text-justify resize-y h-40 w-full border border-[#464343]" placeholder="Text..." <%= isReadOnly ? 'readonly' : '' %>><%= application.env_waste || '' %>  ></textarea>
            </form>           
          </div>

          <div class="text-right text-sm mt-3 text-white pr-5 lg:pr-10">
            <% if (isReadOnly) { %>
              <a href="/environment_supporting_documents?readOnly=true&applicationId=<%= application._id %>" 
                 class="inline-block text-center py-2 w-32 px-3 bg-[#00A19A] text-white rounded-md shadow-lg hover:bg-[#03857e] transition ease-in-out delay-150 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-110 animate-bounce">
                Next
              </a>
            <% } else { %>
              <button id="submit_btn" onclick="updateEnvironmentWaste()"
                class="py-2 px-3 hover:bg-[#03857e] w-32 rounded-md shadow-lg bg-[#00A19A] transition ease-in-out delay-150 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-110 hover:animate-none animate-bounce duration-300">
                Save
             </button>
            <% } %>
          </div>
        </div>  
      </div>  
    </div>  
    <script defer src="https://unpkg.com/alpinejs@3.10.2/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>

    <script src="/javascripts/environment/environment_waste.js"></script>
  </body>   
</html> 

